name: From Nature To Wildfires // Portal Series #1
description:
Turkey has been fighting wildfires for days. Many forests and natural habitats were burned to ashes. People lost their homes, agricultural fields, animals and most importantly their lives due to the fire.

This OBJKT has been donated for hiceturco's #helpetnunc event. All the profits will go to those in need and will help to rebuild and regrow what was lost.

'2021
